description: I Don’t Give a Fork is a Delaware based food cart dedicated to serving delicious and easy-to-eat food to college students and faculty in Wilmington. Specializing in sandwiches for both breakfast and lunch,  I Don’t Give a Fork’s objective is to provide the market with food for the long term. Their goal is to serve food with not only high quality ingredients, but with personality as well.
name: I Don't Give A Fork
